If you haven’t done so already, please take a moment out of your busy day to register to vote. The deadline is 11:59pm on Monday 22nd May.

If you don’t register, you can’t vote. And if you don’t vote, you’ll be unable to legitimately bitch and moan about “the state of this country” for the next five years.

And there's a good chance the country will be in a right fucking state.

Registering only takes a minute. We’ve temporarily replaced the link in our bio — click on it, and let’s participate in a little thing called democracy.

Thank you.
✔#register #election #boxlogo #bogo
